<plot>Anbuchelvan is part of a group of four officers who work for a special squad of plainclothes officers battling organized crime in Chennai. Violent and laconic, he finds little patience for a personal life, until he turns hero in the eyes of dotty schoolteacher Maya, and embarks on a little romance. Meanwhile, his squad kills the brother of a reckless criminal Pandiyan, but fails to wipe off the entire gang. Pandiyan's boys then take the battle into the homes of the officers, going after their family members one by one.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?283480</url></doc>
